    "description": "这是汉堡店的计划建筑工地。<br>爱丽丝有足够的意志力。<br>“我一定会让这家店生意兴隆。”<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >准备各种菜单</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831340/extras/2b32b608a276e47b383c758347b437ef.poster.avif?t=1769935727\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831340/extras/2b32b608a276e47b383c758347b437ef.webm?t=1769935727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831340/extras/2b32b608a276e47b383c758347b437ef.mp4?t=1769935727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831340/extras/79074f2d725f16ce5805ff005e7bf71f.avif?t=1769935727\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>经营汉堡店的模拟游戏。<br></li><li>增加店铺面积，选择摆放桌椅、装饰品<br></li><li>雇用和分配员工。 员工通过工作成长和提高他们的熟练程度<br></li><li>开发提供的菜单<br></li><li>提高您的声誉并以受欢迎的商店为目标<br></li><li>不同的顾客有不同的喜欢的菜肴和室内装饰</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >繁华的商店</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831340/extras/f99c85b517b6251c446bf9bfbd9361d1.poster.avif?t=1769935727\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831340/extras/f99c85b517b6251c446bf9bfbd9361d1.webm?t=1769935727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831340/extras/f99c85b517b6251c446bf9bfbd9361d1.mp4?t=1769935727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >安排桌子、椅子和装饰品</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/18313